ygData.messageBody:
Well I contacted EQ support with all of my info and they said that
they do not support some of the systems that I have. Sooo, I guess
this means that I have to upgrade. Oh well. I know where I can get a
decent computer for my old one as they buy old systems. I am also
keeping my hard drive so I don't have to back-up and reinstall
everything. I have a friend that is going to give me a ride to work
tonight and we are going to stop at the comp shop to check it out.
I'll let ya'll know how that goes and how soon I can be playing again
ok? The Raven P.S. Ya I did have a few programs running when I did
the dxdiag. I think there were like 6? 8?
